span class=\"px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 rounded-full text-sm font-medium\">Elijah</span><span class=\"px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 rounded-full text-sm font-medium\">Isaac</span><span class=\"px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 rounded-full text-sm font-medium\">Rebecca</span><span class=\"px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 rounded-full text-sm font-medium\">Michael</span></div><a class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-medium text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-700\" href=\"/names/islamic/origin/hebrew/1\">Explore <!-- -->Hebrew Names<!-- --> names<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-right w-4 h-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m9 18 6-6-6-6\"></path></svg></a></div></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-100 overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300\"><div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-500 to-purple-600 p-6 text-white\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-globe w-8 h-8\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"M12 2a14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0 20 14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0-20\"></path><path d=\"M2 12h20\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-sm font-medium bg-white/20 px-3 py-1 rounded-full\">5,000<!-- -->+ names</span></div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold mb-2\">Greek Names</h3><p class=\"text-sm opacity-90 leading-relaxed\">Classical names from ancient Greece, many adopted into Christian saints and early church traditions. Known for their elegant sounds.</p></div><div class=\"p-6\"><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4\"><span class=\"px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 rounded-full text-sm font-medium\">Sophia</span><span class=\"px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 rounded-full text-sm font-medium\">Alexander</span><span class=\"px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 rounded-full text-sm font-medium\">Theodore</span><span class=\"px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 rounded-full text-sm font-medium\">Chloe</span><span class=\"px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 rounded-full text-sm font-medium\">Lucas</span><span class=\"px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 rounded-full text-sm font-medium\">Maria</span><span class=\"px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 rounded-full text-sm font-medium\">Andrew</span><span class=\"px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 rounded-full text-sm font-medium\">Helena</span></div><a class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-medium text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-700\" href=\"/names/islamic/origin/greek/1\">Explore <!-- -->Greek Names<!-- --> names<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-right w-4 h-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m9 18 6-6-6-6\"></path></svg></a></div></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-100 overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300\"><div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-500 to-indigo-600 p-6 text-white\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-moon w-8 h-8\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20.985 12.486a9 9 0 1 1-9.473-9.472c.405-.022.617.46.402.803a6 6 0 0 0 8.268 8.268c.344-.215.825-.004.803.401\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-sm font-medium bg-white/20 px-3 py-1 rounded-full\">3,000<!-- -->+ names</span></div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold mb-2\">Persian Names</h3><p class=\"text-sm opacity-90 leading-relaxed\">Names from Persian and Farsi linguistic traditions, popular in Islamic cultures. These names blend Arabic and Iranian influences.</p></div><div class=\"p-6\"><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4\"><span class=\"px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 rounded-full text-sm font-medium\">Kian</span><span class=\"px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 rounded-full text-sm font-medium\">Roxana</span><span class=\"px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 rounded-full text-sm font-medium\">Darius</span><span class=\"px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 rounded-full text-sm font-medium\">Soraya</span><span class=\"px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 rounded-full text-sm font-medium\">Kamran</span><span class=\"px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 rounded-full text-sm font-medium\">Laleh</span><span class=\"px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 rounded-full text-sm font-medium\">Arash</span><span class=\"px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 rounded-full text-sm font-medium\">Tara</span></div><a class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-medium text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-700\" href=\"/names/islamic/origin/persian/1\">Explore <!-- -->Persian Names<!-- --> names<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-right w-4 h-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m9 18 6-6-6-6\"></path></svg></a></div></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-100 overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300\"><div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-teal-500 to-teal-600 p-6 text-white\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-heart w-8 h-8\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M2 9.5a5.5 5.5 0 0 1 9.591-3.676.56.56 0 0 0 .818 0A5.49 5.49 0 0 1 22 9.5c0 2.29-1.5 4-3 5.5l-5.492 5.313a2 2 0 0 1-3 .019L5 15c-1.5-1.5-3-3.2-3-5.5\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-sm font-medium bg-white/20 px-3 py-1 rounded-full\">2,500<!-- -->+ names</span></div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold mb-2\">Turkish Names</h3><p class=\"text-sm opacity-90 leading-relaxed\">Traditional Turkic names adopted into Islamic culture, with Ottoman and Central Asian influences.</p></div><div class=\"p-6\"><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4\"><span class=\"px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 rounded-full text-sm font-medium\">Deniz</span><span class=\"px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 rounded-full text-sm font-medium\">Berk</span><span class=\"px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 rounded-full text-sm font-medium\">Elif</span><span class=\"px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 rounded-full text-sm font-medium\">Can</span><span class=\"px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 rounded-full text-sm font-medium\">Asli</span><span class=\"px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 rounded-full text-sm font-medium\">Yusuf</span><span class=\"px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 rounded-full text-sm font-medium\">Zeynep</span><span class=\"px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 rounded-full text-sm font-medium\">Ahmet</span></div><a class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-medium text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-700\" href=\"/names/islamic/origin/turkish/1\">Explore <!-- -->Turkish Names<!-- --> names<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-right w-4 h-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m9 18 6-6-6-6\"></path></svg></a></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"py-12 sm:py-16 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-50 to-slate-50/30\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-12 text-center\">Names by Origin FAQ</h2><div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6\"><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-200 p-6\"><h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3\">Why does origin matter in baby naming?</h3><p class=\"text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed\">A name&#x27;s origin provides cultural and linguistic context. Understanding where a name comes from helps you appreciate its full meaning and significance, ensuring respectful usage.</p></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-200 p-6\"><h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3\">Can I choose a name outside my culture?</h3><p class=\"text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed\">Yes, many families choose names from different cultures. The key is understanding the meaning, pronunciation, and cultural significance to honor the name&#x27;s heritage.</p></div></div></div></section><section class=\"py-12 sm:py-16 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-600 to-teal-600\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto text-center\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6\">Discover Names from Around the World</h2><p class=\"text-lg text-emerald-100 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto\">Explore 60,000+ verified baby names from Arabic, Sanskrit, Hebrew, Greek, Persian, and Turkish origins. Find the perfect name that connects to cultural heritage.</p><a class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-8 py-4 bg-white text-emerald-600 rounded-xl font-bold text-lg hover:bg-emerald-50 transition-all shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl\" href=\"/names/religion/islamic/1\">Browse All Names</a></div></section></div></main></div><script>$RB=[];$RV=function(a){$RT=performance.now();for(var b=0;b<a.length;b+=2){var c=a[b],e=a[b+1];null!==e.parentNode&&e.parentNode.removeChi